---
title: 安裝執行 — phaseExecute 8 步
description: 備份 → 設定 → 安裝 → 生成 → 打包 → 驗證
links:
  - setup-main: 返回主流程
  - config-protection: 配置保護鏈
---
flowchart TD
    E1["[1/8] 完整備份現有配置
    ─────────────────
    ~/.claude/commands, agents, rules
    ~/.claude/hooks.json, settings.json, keybindings.json
    ~/.zshrc, ~/.zshrc.local, ~/.ripgreprc
    ~/.zsh/modules/
    → dist/backup/YYYY-MM-DD/"]
    E1 --> E2

    E2["[2/8] 全局配置 → ~/.claude/
    ─────────────────
    settings.json — smart merge permissions
    hooks/slack-dispatch.sh — Slack 分發器"]
    E2 --> E3

    E3["[3/8] Claude 安裝 → ~/.claude/
    ─────────────────
    commands (smartSelect 選擇)
    agents (smartSelect 選擇)
    rules (smartSelect 或 fixed)
    hooks (smartSelect 選擇)
    manifest MD5 追蹤"]
    E3 --> E4

    E4["[4/8] ECC + Stacks (並行)
    ─────────────────
    ECC: 外部 commands/agents/rules 融合
    Stacks: 技術棧規則生成 (scan.mjs)"]
    E4 --> E5

    E5["[5/8] CLAUDE.md 生成
    ─────────────────
    per-repo AI 生成 (role → 模板)
    main: 完整版 / temp: 精簡版 / tool: 最小版
    → ~/.claude/projects/{encoded}/CLAUDE.md"]
    E5 --> E6

    E6["[6/8] Plugin 打包
    ─────────────────
    ab-claude-dev.plugin → dist/release/
    ab-slack-message.plugin → dist/release/"]
    E6 --> E7

    E7["[7/8] zsh 模組安裝
    ─────────────────
    modules/*.zsh → ~/.zsh/modules/
    zshrc → ~/.zshrc (個人設定 → .zshrc.local)
    ripgreprc (已有則跳過)"]
    E7 --> E8

    E8["[8/8] 驗證安裝完整性
    ─────────────────
    檢查所有已安裝檔案是否就位
    驗證 settings.json / hooks.json
    驗證 CLAUDE.md (per-repo)
    缺失 → Slack 警告通知"]
